</li><li> Lincoln is an extremely powerful ghost in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/AGirlAndHerFed" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/AGirlAndHerFed">A Girl and Her Fed</a></em>. And <a class="urllink" href="http://agirlandherfed.com/1.1425.html">a Troper<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>
